    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Zero-Gravity 3D Billiards Set in Space</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smash planets across the solar system and sink them into the black hole.<br>Experience a whole new kind of billiards where gravity is gone and space expands in all directions — a fusion of <strong>Zero-Gravity × Space × 3D</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137000/extras/3c08ade8c4ea643a146f8b556b6c69e0.avif?t=1754407244\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Space Phenomena That Shape the Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use cosmic forces to your advantage:<br><strong>Heliopause</strong> launches planets forward on entry,<br><strong>Asteroids</strong> slow them down on impact,<br>and an expanding <strong>Black Hole</strong> reshapes the battlefield itself.<br>In this game, the universe decides your next move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137000/extras/b359141c187a437144c249307087c99f.avif?t=1754407244\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Multiple Rules &amp; Local Multiplayer up to 4 Players</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From a simple rule set where players compete to sink the most planets,<br>to a turn-based Nineball-style challenge — choose your rules and master the field.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports <strong>up to 4 players in local multiplayer</strong>.<br>Dive into the world of <strong>zero-gravity space billiards</strong> again and again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137000/extras/d5fb733f29a3c9ae6c004ebe164543c2.avif?t=1754407244\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Stream</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PlanetStrike fully supports all players as recorders of the cosmos.<br>Feel free to stream, upload, and monetize gameplay on platforms like YouTube, Twitch, or anywhere else.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No need for advance permission.<br>Just strike, and let your moments echo across the stars.</p>",
